<p><b>Beryl</b> was a <a href="/wiki/Compositing_window_manager" title="Compositing window manager">compositing window manager</a> for the <a href="/wiki/X_Window_System" title="X Window System">X Window System</a> which <a href="/wiki/Fork_(software_development)" title="Fork (software development)">forked</a> from <a href="/wiki/Compiz" title="Compiz">Compiz</a> in September 2006 and was re-merged in 2007<sup id="cite_ref-BerylCompizMerge_0-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-BerylCompizMerge-0" title=""><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup>, under the name of <a href="/wiki/Compiz_Fusion" title="Compiz Fusion">Compiz Fusion</a>.</p>
